figure.figDesc: Scan of a pencil drawing. Depicts two figures in a vehicle facing the left of the page. The figure on the left side of the vehicle is facing the driver. The driver of the vehicle is leaning forward against a steering wheel, almost outside of the windshield and right door. Back of the scan is blank.
